HomePage.niggaonetenq: Gumstar is not just chewing gum, it is a success story based on love for its business and the pursuit of impeccable quality. Since 2016, we have been giving people fresh breath and bright taste experiences, constantly improving technology and expanding our range. Starting with 15 people, today Gumstar is a well-coordinated team of 100 professionals dedicated to their work. Fully automated production that meets international standards guarantees the impeccable quality of each chewing gum. We successfully cooperate and implement the latest technologies and equipment in 7 leading countries of the world: Germany, Switzerland, France, Turkey, India, Malaysia and China.
